          MODULE=logwatch
         VERSION=7.15
          SOURCE=$MODULE-$VERSION.tar.gz
      SOURCE_URL=$SFORGE_URL/logwatch
        WEB_SITE=http://www.logwatch.org
      SOURCE_VFY=sha256:5913783d52fe02a18fd796acee2335eeca43cb17e913eca33e2f211e64f2fcdb
         ENTERED=20040913
         UPDATED=20260723
           SHORT="Monitor log files realtime"

cat << EOF
Logwatch is a customizable log analysis system. Logwatch parses through your
system's logs for a given period of time and creates a report analyzing areas
that you specify, in as much detail as you require. Logwatch is easy to use
and will work right out of the package on most systems.
EOF
